videos.headline: TCU gets on the board early with rushing TD
videos.description: Kenny Hill scrambles for a 7-yard touchdown as TCU takes a 7-0 lead over Kansas State.

videos.headline: TCU fumble leads to KSU field goal
videos.description: Running back Darius Anderson rushes to the right and has the ball stripped, leading to a Kansas State 38-yard field goal.

videos.headline: TCU extends lead with TD run
videos.description: Running back Sewo Olonilua takes a direct snap and runs up the middle for a 1 yard touchdown, as TCU leads Kansas State 20-3.
